    "Socket.IO is a library that enables protocol sharing and transport through the use of WebSockets (W3C, 2023a) to transfer information between a client and server and is used for building applications that require instant interactions and updates between a server and client(s) in a bidirectional manner (Socket. IO, 2023)."
  ]
